Class VariationPaletteItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.designer.model.VariationPaletteItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PaletteItem

    public class VariationPaletteItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements PaletteItem
    Implementation of a PaletteItem which delegates to another PaletteItem but which possibly overrides the title, icon and or creation properties.
